{"tid":1321662,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[伏中之伏]有冇人去過X-Salons Group剪頭髮？","createTime":"2019-07-15T17:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T18:33:38.000Z","uid":122431,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ad5f102c4d2cce5369f931f3f2d44b5c95844f6f","tid":1321662,"uid":122431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:27:25.000Z","msg":"話說上個禮拜book咗X-Salons Group尖沙咀門市整頭髮，join咗2人同行套餐，染髮+剪髮 $298。<br />\n<br />\n一去到係冇人理我地，要主動問可唔可以睇色版。揀顏色嘅時候我地有問意見，髮型師好撚串答你<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每一隻色都要漂先上到，如果你堅持要做嘅我寧願你唔好喺度整</span></strong></span>之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每一句都好有骨咁疾住曬，又話你個頭自己染過乜柒都上唔到色etc 總之要串到你一幢都冇。最後揀好色，叫佢修一修髮尾，佢用半分鐘剪完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後就開始上色。<br />\n<br />\n洗頭嗰陣淨係用洗頭水+護髮素各洗咗一次，求9其洗完就算，正常都會用洗頭水洗兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n吹完頭出到嚟係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上到色嘅</span></span></strong>，所以個肥婆都唔敢講啲咩上唔到色，吹完頭之後直接問你使唔使揸髮尾油就算，問佢可唔可以吹一吹個髮尾，即刻勁撚串話「你做得呢啲色(染灰)一加熱就會甩晒啲色，如果你OK嘅我咪幫你做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」我堅持叫佢做少少styling，佢就勁撚Hea咁樣嘅夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後搞掂唔會俾鏡你照，淨係講左句: 「你除咗件袍俾我」，仲直接響我全朵，問：你就係book時間嗰個XXX?」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小姐都冇加句。<br />\n<br />\n同行友人經驗比我更差，另一個肥婆仲串，態度串過馬撚。<br />\n<br />\n呢個salons group一直都有做好多套餐，同埋俾好評會有優惠，所以Facebook個好評係刷出黎嘅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZBcLLn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZBcLLn.png&h=b2c308ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n Red Hair Salon 地址: 九龍尖沙咀赫德道11A至11D 1樓 <br />\n2個肥婆串柒柒，俾錢買難受，咪撚去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718524790a8891165218b4caf34bc70068aaec67","tid":1321662,"uid":122431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:36:31.000Z","msg":"同行友人預備染髮嘅時候，坐嘅位有啲熱出緊汗，要求較大少少冷氣<br />\n肥婆：怕你凍親喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n友人：我出汗喎<br />\n肥婆：唔啦琴日先有客較完冷氣又話凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n友人：如果凍就可以教返高個溫度<br />\n肥婆：唔啦搞嚟搞去咁煩<br />\n<br />\n之後染完，吹完頭完全冇諗住幫你剪，要主動提出想剪先幫你，仲要串9你之前個髮型師幫你<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">剪反曬個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>，唔撚肯剪，仲要話<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「你個頭好似剪完冇耐咋喎」</span></span></strong>，關你撚事？仲恐嚇你再剪短要剷青㗎啦喎（我朋友係女）"},{"pid":"b3c08d30933280f231a8005e5c27aa7b62c1988c","tid":1321662,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:37:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"800a4e0a2e77092e3eb9e3bba5e034918589a673","tid":1321662,"uid":122431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b3c08d30933280f231a8005e5c27aa7b62c1988c","tid":1321662,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:37:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:39:05.000Z","msg":"而家FB IG嗰啲太多廣告，勁撚易中伏"},{"pid":"0f2f57ec9db611046546e71af37f5eeae9ab8aa4","tid":1321662,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:39:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2c39189eccf3ae58bcd26c497abfbe3fde32364","tid":1321662,"uid":237177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:40:14.000Z","msg":"元朗ok wor 態度好好 手腳快<br />\n我染髮佢仲再三提醒我如果染過黑色係上唔到色"},{"pid":"9e7a2c9f0e19c49e264ea317963adf11fc3026cd","tid":1321662,"uid":122431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e2c39189eccf3ae58bcd26c497abfbe3fde32364","tid":1321662,"uid":237177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:40:14.000Z","msg":"元朗ok wor 態度好好 手腳快<br />\n我染髮佢仲再三提醒我如果染過黑色係上唔到色"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:42:20.000Z","msg":"之前有朋友都係去過尖沙咀，同樣都係個肥婆serve，態度又係極之差，每句說話都有骨<br />\n我都係貪平，諗住快手整一整個頭髮型師係點都無所謂，點知一肚氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee77f9d76a9a0d58efe50000d2279cfcd2f12da3","tid":1321662,"uid":237177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e7a2c9f0e19c49e264ea317963adf11fc3026cd","tid":1321662,"uid":122431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e2c39189eccf3ae58bcd26c497abfbe3fde32364","tid":1321662,"uid":237177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:40:14.000Z","msg":"元朗ok wor 態度好好 手腳快<br />\n我染髮佢仲再三提醒我如果染過黑色係上唔到色"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:42:20.000Z","msg":"之前有朋友都係去過尖沙咀，同樣都係個肥婆serve，態度又係極之差，每句說話都有骨<br />\n我都係貪平，諗住快手整一整個頭髮型師係點都無所謂，點知一肚氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:44:15.000Z","msg":"元朗overall 成間鋪都好friendly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女仔個個仲好貼心 俾水係俾暖水我"},{"pid":"5ebf1431e191fa2bc3131d0ae12dbbb57fd87b57","tid":1321662,"uid":8955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:50:13.000Z","msg":"屌我之前都去過旺角嗰間，sell得好勁，最後同個fd都加多咗幾舊水整頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d769cb69322f8231cabf1aeadba1b5b00db4aea7","tid":1321662,"uid":122431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ebf1431e191fa2bc3131d0ae12dbbb57fd87b57","tid":1321662,"uid":8955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:50:13.000Z","msg":"屌我之前都去過旺角嗰間，sell得好勁，最後同個fd都加多咗幾舊水整頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:53:22.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀呢間嗰兩個肥婆唔憂做，sell都廢撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823f1d0b2c2da2a3533670141a59c2d8597d1baa","tid":1321662,"uid":122431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee77f9d76a9a0d58efe50000d2279cfcd2f12da3","tid":1321662,"uid":237177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e7a2c9f0e19c49e264ea317963adf11fc3026cd","tid":1321662,"uid":122431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e2c39189eccf3ae58bcd26c497abfbe3fde32364","tid":1321662,"uid":237177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:40:14.000Z","msg":"元朗ok wor 態度好好 手腳快<br />\n我染髮佢仲再三提醒我如果染過黑色係上唔到色"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:42:20.000Z","msg":"之前有朋友都係去過尖沙咀，同樣都係個肥婆serve，態度又係極之差，每句說話都有骨<br />\n我都係貪平，諗住快手整一整個頭髮型師係點都無所謂，點知一肚氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:44:15.000Z","msg":"元朗overall 成間鋪都好friendly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女仔個個仲好貼心 俾水係俾暖水我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:55:35.000Z","msg":"佢旗下啲salon參差不齊，同埋佢哋好注重做之前要帶頭盔，因為佢哋公司好似做衰咗可以免費整過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以個肥婆先串柒柒叫人唔好染啲有機會fail嘅色，仲開到口叫你可以唔使喺度整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b59c25d5d91d768f5a6e2bc89bfa9ef1fb72ea","tid":1321662,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:17:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6aa44966affc5a534608455b6cee2257cff839ca","tid":1321662,"uid":196922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:27:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4617a0f1fc9f432a19366fd383860ae0cdc31943","tid":1321662,"uid":122431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aa44966affc5a534608455b6cee2257cff839ca","tid":1321662,"uid":196922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:27:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:29:42.000Z","msg":"仲要串9我上一個髮型師幫我上到色係因為佢啲染料多化學成分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d505610b35042e99ce193340b4f1895808219586","tid":1321662,"uid":37976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"咁你有無叫佢幫你補做？<br />\n去第二間體驗應該好啲"},{"pid":"93863afb36