ets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0720b626bcdda2ca8cc2326d7f2d5ba9a8930157","tid":1321662,"uid":196456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:59:08.000Z","msg":"早排去完旺角royale hair salon 搵Jun Kwan 整頭 <br />\n<br />\n終極差評！千奇唔好去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先間店好污糟！啲鏡十年冇抹過！去到水又冇..<br />\n洗頭洗到啲水飛曬去我塊面到 仲要之後同熟客好大聲咁討論其他客人。我見佢對客人咁多不滿 我都心知不妙，所以全程冇出過聲，默默地等佢得閒先幫我整..<br />\n<br />\n挽電話挽左幾個鐘，諗住睇下雜誌 一攞上手....本書上面舊塵厚撚到...<br />\n<br />\n之後佢幫我洗完頭就問我分界起邊 我米指比佢睇 咁佢問得我 我諗條分界都重要 見佢分得太多 米自己攞手指分番好佢 之後佢無啦啦比把梳我 同我講 叫我自己分 我即刻呆撚左望住佢。<br />\n其實我全程都冇出過聲 時間又係就你 又冇同你講價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我諗我都唔算麻煩客 都唔明佢啲態度係發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重點都唔算平間野<br />\n<br />\nP.s.其實仲有其他受氣 但太零碎 廢事講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gVA5uO4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgVA5uO4.png&h=8a6bb2cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好後悔自己做咩唔上網睇負評先去<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkhairsalon.com/shop/view.php?sid=3019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkhairsalon.com%2Fshop%2Fview.php%3Fsid%3D3019&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cEyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=0c24c0a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkhairsalon.com/shop/view.php?sid=3019</a>"},{"pid":"b144e71dd5806ae0a40e01412b4ef7909eccb69f","tid":1321662,"uid":122431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3e28c0aac1a4c32f43c7821b8d96bcaebb95cdf","tid":1321662,"uid":78770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:54:40.000Z","msg":"人生第一次電髮就係哩間salons group嘅將軍澳店做<br />\n電完之後馬上直返同冇電過冇分別<br />\n結果一星期內要去補電<br />\n補電之後把頭髮就傷哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201